Wes Craven's New Nightmare;;66;;80;;R;;Reality and fantasy meet in unsettling ways in this installment of the long-running horror series, which finds director Wes Craven and actors Heather Langenkamp and Robert Englund all portraying themselves. As Heather (Heather Langenkamp) considers making another film with Craven, her son, Dylan (Miko Hughes), falls under the spell of the iconic disfigured villain Freddy Krueger (Robert Englund). Eventually, Langenkamp must confront Freddy's demonic spirit to save the soul of Dylan.;;Horror;;Wes Craven;;1994;;Robert Englund,Heather Langenkamp,Miko Hughes,David Newsom,Tracy Middendorf,Fran Bennett,John Saxon,Wes Craven,Robert Shaye,Sara Risher,Marianne Maddalena;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wes_cravens_new_nightmare